mber 1 salary and used for the following calendar year for employees hired after september 1 their salary is frozen for benefits purposes on their date of hire and that amount is used for the remainder of the year of hire and the entire following year basic life insurance you automatically receive coverage equal to your salary up to a $50000 maximum supplemental life insurance you may purchase supplemental life insurance from one to eight times your salary up to a $1 million maximum if you purchase coverage levels that are more than three times your salary or if you did not enroll when you were first eligible you must complete evidence of insurability proof of good health questions you do this when you make your election online supplemental dependent life insurance you may purchase coverage for your spouse or registered domestic partner up to a maximum of 50 of your combined basic and supplemental coverage or $250000 whichever is less coverage over $25000 requires evidence of insurability you can also select coverage of $5000 $10000 or $25000 for your child ren as long as you have at least twice as much coverage for yourself accidental death & dismemberment ad&d insurance ad&d insurance provides you and your family with protection against accidental death or loss of limb or body function it does not pay a benefit for a death arising from illness or natural causes you may purchase ad&d insurance from one to eight times your salary up to a $1 million maximum for you and or you and your children coverage is also available for your spouse or registered domestic partner business travel accident insurance stanford's business travel accident insurance plan pays a benefit if you are accidentally injured or die during an official university business trip enrollment is automatic and stanford pays the full cost of coverage for more information go to the risk management web site workers compensation worker's compensation provides benefits for work related illness or injury stanford continues to pay your academic base salary for the first five working days after a work related accident and then workers compensation payment starts for more information go to the risk management web site quick links risk management web site resources what women need to know about life insurance how much life insurance do you need ad&d faq basic life insurance faq supplemental life insurance faq contacts prudential insurance company of america tel 800 524 0542 home benefits overview medical & life retirement resource library contacts mybenefits site map how to use this site human resources stanford university stanford university terms of use copyright complaints document download
